{"tid":563621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"調查:「Apple用家討厭約會對象用Android」！","createTime":"2018-02-17T06:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-17T10:59:14.000Z","uid":72009,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"529ec54237d66b70cd48ce41c8b9545f404a516c","tid":563621,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T06:22:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://外國交友網站Match.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%A4%E5%8F%8B%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99Match.com&d=825nkqZtgwYwYKRIcmS6AsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=87e74ea8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">外國交友網站Match.com</a>的一項以科技產品（如手機）及約會的關係在美國進行民意調查，受訪18歲至70歲的單身人士。經過多番整理資料後，得出了不少出人意表的結果，發現若然約會雙方分別是iOS和Andriod用家時，大家對對方有負面印象的機率都大大提高。iOS用家對Andriod用家做出負面評價的機會更比平均水平高出21倍！可見iOS和Andriod的戰爭，可不是在兩家公司的商業層面上，更滲透至人們生活的指標。<br />\n<br />\n用新手機印象會較好<br />\n另外，手機的新舊程度也足以影響對方對你的印象，研究顯示有92％的女性覺得手機型號新舊對約會印象有影響，不喜歡約會對象使用太老舊的手機。小編亦覺得合理，選擇手機也能顯示一個人的品味，有如衣著一般。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nmplus.hk/social-buzz/約會-android-apple/4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nmplus.hk%2Fsocial-buzz%2F%E7%B4%84%E6%9C%83-android-apple%2F4%2F&d=825nkqZtgwYwYKRIcmS6AsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=02e86254\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nmplus.hk/social-buzz/約會-android-apple/4/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"485cb40ec6a722d21a054c1dfc6378e9e51bb795","tid":563621,"uid":25866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T06:26:23.000Z","msg":"如果小米撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d14702ea6c7f66d5da1ab919829a05b2119ae1","tid":563621,"uid":22553,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T06:37:34.000Z","msg":"如果對象係靚仔靚女就話知你用3310啦"},{"pid":"2f1c806d4e1b40f270ea5741fbad5f272fe78a98","tid":563621,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi